期刊論文


吳進欽、薑忠信、侯育銘 （2005）自閉症兒童的立即模仿與延遲模仿之研究。中華心理衛生，18，01-24。


Chung-Hsin Chiang, Chin-Chin, Wu, & Chi-Hua Lee (2005). Early Social Communication and Cognitive Abilities in Young Children with Autism. Journal of Policy and Practice in Intellectual Disabilities, No.2, pp.205.


Chin-Chin, Wu & Chung-Hsin Chiang (2005). Cognitive Competence in Young Children with Autism. Journal of Policy and Practice in Intellectual Disabilities, No.2, pp.217-218.


薑忠信、吳進欽、李季樺 （2006）自閉症兒童的象徵遊戲能力：縱貫研究。中華心理學刊，48，255-273。


蔣蕙如、薑忠信、侯育銘、吳進欽（2008）早產兒之詞彙能力發展。中華心理衛生，21，407-440。


吳進欽、薑忠信、侯育銘、劉俊宏 （2009）自閉症類幼童發展能力表現型態之研究。中華心理衛生，22，01-25。


吳進欽、薑忠信、虞燕婷（2010）。自閉症類幼兒社會註意力的探究。中華心理學刊，52，57-74。


Chin-Chin Wu, Chung-Hsin Chiang, & Yuh-Ming Hou (2011). A Two Time Point Study of Imitative Abilities in Children with Autism Spectrum Disorders. Journal of Applied Research in Intellectual Disabilities, 24, 39-49.（SSCI）


吳進欽、薑忠信（2011）。自閉症類幼兒標準化發展測驗的表現。應用心理研究，51，15-40。


薑忠信、吳進欽（2012）。自閉症幼兒心理病理學研究的探索。應用心理研究，52，16-19。


薑忠信、吳進欽、劉俊宏、侯育銘（2012）。2-3歲自閉症幼兒篩檢量表的發展：T-STAT的初究。中華心理衛生學刊，25，135-154。(TSSCI)


吳進欽、薑忠信、侯育銘、劉俊宏、朱慶琳（2012）。T-STAT評估學齡前自閉症類兒童效度的探究。教育與心理研究，35，81-98。(TSSCI)


朱慶琳、薑忠信、黃宜珊、吳進欽（2012）。學齡前自閉症類兒童的適應行為型態。中華心理學刊, 54, 349-364.


Chung-Hsin Chiang, Chin-Chin Wu, Yuh-Ming Hou, Ching-Lin Chu, Jiun-Horng Liu, & Wei-Tsuen Soong. (in press). "Development of T-STAT for Early Autism Screening," Journal of Autism and Developmental Disorders.


研討會論文


Chin-Chin Wu, & Chung-Hsin Chiang (2004). "The immediate and deferred imitation in children with autism." International Meeting for Autism Research.


薑忠信、吳進欽、侯育銘 （2005）. "自閉症兒童有模仿能力的缺陷嗎？一項縱貫研究的初步觀察,"第四十四屆 台灣心理學年會. 桃園，台灣。


Chung-Hsin Chiang, Chi-Hua Lee, & Chin-Chin Wu (2005). "Can young children with autism use gestures and objects as symbol?" International Meeting for Autism Research.


Chin-Chin Wu, Chung-Hsin Chiang, & Yuh-Ming, Hou (2006).  "A style of imitation deficit in children with autism." The International Society on Infant Studies (ISIS).


侯育銘、劉俊宏、薑忠信、吳進欽（2007）. "發展年齡對自閉症早期診斷的影響," 第十屆台灣兒童青少年精神醫學會年會及第二屆海峽兩岸兒童青少年精神醫學會. 臺北，台灣。


薑忠信、吳進欽、侯育銘、劉俊宏（2007）. "發展台灣2-3歲自閉症幼兒篩檢工具：初步資料的分析," 第十屆台灣兒童青少年精神醫學會年會及第二屆海峽兩岸兒童青少年精神醫學會。 臺北，台灣。


吳進欽、薑忠信、侯育銘、劉俊宏（2007）. "自閉症幼兒發展能力表現型態," 第十屆台灣兒童青少年精神醫學會年會及第二屆海峽兩岸兒童青少年精神醫學會. 臺北，台灣。


劉俊宏、侯育銘、薑忠信、吳進欽（2007）. "DSM-IV診斷準則應用於幼兒廣泛性發展疾患臨床診斷的描述性分析," 第十屆台灣兒童青少年精神醫學會年會及第二屆海峽兩岸兒童青少年精神醫學會。 臺北，台灣。


Chin-Chin Wu, Chung-Hsin Chiang, Yuh-Ming, Hou, & Jiun-Horng Liu (2007). "Developmental profiles in young children with autism spectrum disorders." International Meeting for Autism Research.


Chung-Hsin Chiang, Chin-Chin Wu, Yuh-Ming, Hou, & Jiun-Horng Liu (2007). "Screening Tool for Autism in Two-Year-Old- Taiwan Version (T-STAT): Development and Preliminary data." International Meeting for Autism Research.


Yuh-Ming Hou, Jiun-Horng Liu, Chung-Hsin Chiang, & Chin-Chin Wu (2008). "Stability of early diagnosis in autism spectrum disorders." International Meeting for Autism Research.


Chung-Hsin Chiang, Chin-Chin Wu, Yuh-Ming, Hou, & Jiun-Horng Liu (2008). "Development of Screening Tool for Autism in Two-Year-Olds Taiwan Version (T-STAT): Development and Preliminary data." International Meeting for Autism Research.


Chin-Chin Wu, Chung-Hsin Chiang, & Yen-Ting Yu, (2009). "Social Orienting, Joint Attention and the Relationship in Young Children With Autism Spectrum Disorders.” Biennial Meeting of Society for Research in child Development.


Chin-Chin Wu, & Chung-Hsin Chiang (2010). “Relationships among joint attention, imitation, play and language in young children with autism." International Meeting for Autism Research.


Chin-Chin Wu, & Chung-Hsin Chiang (2011). “The Developmental Sequence of Social-Communicative Skills in Young Children with Autism: A Longitudinal Study." 10th International Meeting for Autism Research.


吳進欽、薑忠信（2011）“自閉症幼兒社會溝通能力發展," 第12屆國際發展遲緩兒童早期療育論文發表大會


Chin-Chin Wu, Chung-Hsin Chiang, & Yuh-Ming, Hou (2012). “Prelinguistic Predictors of Language in Young Children with Autism Spectrum Disorders." 11th International Meeting for Autism Research.


吳進欽、薑忠信、朱慶琳、侯育銘（2012）“自閉症類幼兒非語言溝通能力和語言與自閉症症狀的關係" 第13屆國際發展遲緩兒童早期療育論文發表大會


